{"tid":1844914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護人員，你肯定係因為你嘅職責而唔肯罷工？","createTime":"2020-01-27T00:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T17:06:48.000Z","uid":27725,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"50da973daa1b74c3e4864b132e295f410983bd9d","tid":1844914,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:07:08.000Z","msg":"事實擺在眼前，你唔肯反抗，只會越來越多香港人有事。<br />\n好明顯社會上大多數人，無論老中青都係支持你哋罷工，都講到明唔會怪你地。<br />\n<br />\n咁點解有啲醫護人員仲唔肯罷工？問心嗰句，你確定你係因為職責所在覺得唔可以dup低啲病人，定係因為你怕事，驚冇咗份工或者秋後算帳啊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢啲嘢唔使同我地交代，你自己知就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a49dbee6a4fc6cd543877864594a9e893480d2","tid":1844914,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:08:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> 香港班醫護仲唔罷工只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港，間接促成社區爆發，害死更多人，包括你自己在內<br />\n<br />\n你地係咪想犧牲自己條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edG0Z6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedG0Z6X.jpg&h=8ac5b79d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03091358234484e7e45882ec1972423ceb56e420","tid":1844914,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:13:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n三罷先係最好既支持方式</span></span>"},{"pid":"813b51677931e7e701fddc36dce806a682b2f207","tid":1844914,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:16:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ceffda90df144e0d46a7fa19769d87ec9ac690f","tid":1844914,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":